Run:
  sudo install -Dm755 nvcheckerTimer /usr/bin/nvcheckerTimer
  sudo install -Dm644 nvchecker.service /usr/lib/systemd/system/nvchecker.service
  sudo install -Dm644 nvchecker.timer /usr/lib/systemd/system/nvchecker.timer
  sudo install -Dm644 nvchecker.cfg /etc/nvchecker/nvchecker.cfg

Then set the nvchecker folder at /etc/nvchecker/nvchecker.cfg,
  If you want to use smtp, alse set path at /usr/bin/nvcheckerTimer
